2026-01-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] 다음 레이드: 그림자 (로아온),https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2677293?p=51&my=chuchu,True,2025-09-19,5,10,4,9,3,3,5,7,10,9,엔드 레이드,raid_update,None,6,"Dark fantasy '그림자' raid (쿠크세이튼 등), new systems; post-winter Q1 timing inferred from 로아온 event, high difficulty drives mat demand, 아크그리드 integration."
