2025-07-01,Stream Summary,[Stream Summary] 2025 Summer-Fall Roadmap Announcement Stream,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,False,2025-08-14,6,7,5,8,6,5,4,7,6,7,Progression Events,general_update,None,8,Stream announcement generates hype and player engagement. Paradise system launch drives demand for progression materials. Valkyrie class release increases cosmetic package sales. Prestige Shop retroactive tracking incentivizes Royal Crystal spending.
2025-07-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Paradise Progression System Launch,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,True,2025-08-14,8,9,4,6,5,6,3,6,4,5,Progression System,system_change,None,9,New seasonal solo progression system designed for global version to accelerate player advancement. Increases honing material supply through three interconnected activities. Reduces daily grind burden by transitioning Una's Tasks to weekly rewards post-reputation completion. Decreases gold sink pressure while maintaining engagement.
2025-08-20,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Valkyrie Advanced Class Release,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,True,2025-08-14,7,8,6,7,7,6,5,8,5,9,Class Release,general_update,None,9,Female Paladin class with Support and DPS build options drives new character creation and cosmetic purchases. Legendary class gift and progression events increase honing material demand. Package volume spike from class-specific cosmetics and skins. Prestige Shop launch with exclusive MVP backgrounds and skins increases monetization.
2025-10-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Kazeros Raid Act 4 & Final Tier Release,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,True,2025-08-14,9,10,8,9,8,7,6,9,9,8,Raid Content,raid_update,None,9,Climactic endgame raid tier with mandatory story quest prerequisite (Destined Trajectory). Ark Grid system integration introduces core farming mechanics. Significant gold sink through Ark Grid gem crafting and fusion. High item level requirements (1720+) drive honing material demand. Challenge and Express events support progression. Extreme Thaemine rematch provides alternative endgame content.
2025-10-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Ark Grid System Implementation,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,True,2025-08-14,6,7,9,10,8,5,7,10,7,6,System Overhaul,system_change,None,9,"Character-bound core system with 6 core types (3 class-exclusive, 3 universal) across 6 variants. Phased slot opening over weeks reduces initial setup burden. Gem crafting with reroll mechanics and fusion system creates sustained gold sink. Essence consolidation from duplicate cores incentivizes long-term engagement. Replaces tripod and epic engraving systems, reducing complexity while increasing customization depth."
2025-10-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] NA Server Merger (East + West),https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,True,2025-08-14,5,6,5,5,4,4,8,3,3,2,Infrastructure,economy_shock,None,8,Server consolidation improves matchmaking and economy health. Character/guild name defaults to highest combat level roster address years of name-squatting. Extensive maintenance downtime and legacy bot data purge. Short-term supply/demand disruption from server instability. Long-term gold inflation from merged economy and increased player density. Reduced immediate package sales due to maintenance window.
2025-11-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] The First Speedrun Competition Event,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/2454082?p=73&my=chuchu,True,2025-08-14,4,5,6,7,5,6,3,5,10,7,Competitive Event,raid_update,None,8,Top 10 speedrun ranking with Ark Grid enabled creates competitive pressure for optimal builds. Shorter expected clear time (5 days vs. Camen's 10 days) reflects increased player skill. Speedrun rewards incentivize high-end gear optimization. Competitive cosmetics and titles drive engagement. Estimated clear time based on internal 'octopus' employee prediction model with high accuracy track record.
2025-05-20,Stream Summary,[Stream Summary] 2025-05-20 Developer Stream,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,False,2025-05-20,4,3,0,0,3,0,2,5,6,7,에스더 보상,general_update,None,9,"Stream announces compensation for Esther users (up to 20 bound 에스더의 기운 based on market price), gradual relic engraving supply increase without gold dup extension, gem unbinding extension to 15 days with attack power removal; creates hype for immediate patches but mixed sentiment due to past apologies and economic regrets; low gold inflation from nerfs, moderate package volume from honors."
2025-05-27,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Next Week Kazeros Raid Nerf (Normal Focus),https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,2,5,0,0,0,0,1,4,4,2,None,raid_update,None,9,"All Kazeros raids (including finale) get normal/hard nerfs: boss HP reduction, damage adjustments, pattern removals, 1 revive per raid; lowers difficulty barrier, reduces gold sink pressure on mid-gear players, slight demand up for raid mats to push clears."
2025-06-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Relic Engraving Gradual Supply Increase,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,0,0,0,0,7,0,3,2,0,0,None,economy_shock,None,8,"No gold dup extension; steady supply ramps (e.g., Act 3+ drops for 1720+); aims to normalize high prices without flooding market, potential engraving supply boost offsets past deflation shocks."
2025-06-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Brilliant Gem Unbinding Changes,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,0,0,5,6,0,0,4,3,0,0,None,system_change,None,8,"15-day unbinding period (from 7), remove extra attack power; eases gem liquidity post-season 3 resets, demand stays high for supports but supply improves slightly, risks inflation from easier swaps."
2025-06-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Combat Analyzer & Total Combat Power Release,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,None,system_change,None,7,"Tools for battle analysis and comprehensive combat power metrics; minor difficulty perception shift via better optimization, neutral economy but enables efficient gearing."
2025-07-01,Roadmap Item,"[Roadmap Item] China Broadcast Features (Honor Rewards, Daily Epona, Codex)",https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,1,0,5,명예보상,general_update,None,7,"Adopt select China features: daily Epona, codex (no ranking/collecting), diverse honors; moderate package influx dilutes rarity slightly."
2025-07-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] 3 Class Balance Patch,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,0,2,0,2,0,1,0,0,3,0,None,system_change,None,8,"Confirmed balance for 3 classes (complex ops, high season 3 diff, overpowered); minor demand shifts in builds, neutral overall."
2025-08-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Supporter Improvements (Summer),https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,0,1,2,3,0,2,0,0,2,0,None,system_change,None,7,"Summer fixes: skills to 10+ levels, mana issues, Ark passive; boosts support viability, slight demand up for support gear."
2025-08-15,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] Difficulty Segmentation & Raid Adjustments,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1995358?p=105&my=chuchu,True,2025-05-20,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,3,5,3,None,raid_update,None,6,"Ongoing: segment difficulties (e.g., Kazeros finale gate 1 easy, gate 2 harder; First only gate 2); 1 revive all raids; eases mid-tier access, moderate gold sink."
2025-04-30,Stream Summary,[Stream Summary] 2025-04-30 Developer Stream,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1822270?p=117&my=chuchu,False,2025-04-30,4,3,7,8,6,2,5,3,5,6,Progression Materials,general_update,None,9,"Stream announces immediate events like 골두꺼비 (hype for honing mats via 유각), 보석 조율 (gem market volatility), 캐릭터 귀속 골드 (growth support, reduces gold circulation), creating short-term hype and uncertainty in gem/engraving markets amid economic recession discussion."
2025-04-30,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] 골두꺼비 출시,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1822270?p=117&my=chuchu,True,2025-04-30,8,4,0,0,0,0,2,4,2,5,Honing Materials,economy_shock,None,10,"4주간 랜덤유각주머니 최대 6개 구매, 천장 시스템 추가. Immediate honing mat influx from 24회 유각뽑기, boosts supply and player progression."
2025-05-07,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] 보석 조율 시스템 추가,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1822270?p=117&my=chuchu,True,2025-04-30,0,0,6,9,0,0,1,5,3,4,System Change,system_change,None,9,"보석 변환 시 캐릭터 귀속 + 스킬/겁작 변환, 프리셋, 추가 공격력 지원. 10겁 보유자 환급 (10겁=8렙 보석 1개). Increases gem demand via conversions, reduces tradeable supply, post-stream gem price volatility noted."
2025-07-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] 캐릭터 귀속 골드 추가,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1822270?p=117&my=chuchu,True,2025-04-30,5,6,0,0,0,0,3,7,4,7,Growth Support,economy_shock,None,8,"여름 모챌익 지정 캐릭터 대량 지원. Non-tradeable gold for new/alt/returnee growth, acts as gold sink reducing inflation while easing progression burden."
