2025-06-01,Roadmap Item,[Roadmap Item] 인당 1회 부활 기능 추가 + 레이드 4난이도,https://www.inven.co.kr/board/lostark/6271/1822270?p=117&my=chuchu,True,2025-04-30,2,7,0,0,0,0,0,2,8,2,Raid Mechanics,raid_update,None,8,"피로도 개선으로 부활 추가, 싱글/노말/하드/최상위 운영. Increases raid participation, raises effective difficulty ceiling but lowers entry barrier, potential demand spike for gear."
